<p>'If they remain as a couple for up to four days, we then give some other singles the chance to enter the cabin and potentially meet their Mr or Miss Right.' </p>

<p>On when the show will hit screens, the source added: 'They'll start filming in the next few months as they're casting now and it will air in the new year.'</p>

